People with disability have been denied the opportunity to register as voters, ODM's Nickson Kakiri has said. The ODM disability league chairman said most of the countries six million PLWDs cannot reach the registration desks. He spoke on Sunday in Kisumu during training for PLWDs leaders and NASA aspirants from Western. &ldquo;In most situations ... the PLWDs are not able to communicate effectively with the clerks to receive help," Kakiri said.